        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I request that you will be so good as to inform the members of the Committee that their wish to name the medal after me is a very great honour, which I gladly accept. It is particularly pleasing to me to have my name connected, in however indirect a manner, with a scheme for advancing science, the study of which has been my chief source of happiness throughout life.<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </div>
        
        
